ing with listings, bookings, or communications on the site.",{"children":"These terms apply to all users, including hosts, producers, scouts, crew members, and anyone browsing or interacting with listings, bookings, or communications on the site."}]]}]]}],["$","section","2. User Accounts",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"2. User Accounts"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","You may need to register for an account to access certain features. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information and to keep that information updated.",{"children":"You may need to register for an account to access certain features. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information and to keep that information updated."}],["$","p","We may require email verification, identity checks, age confirmation, or additional screening before enabling certain account functions, listings, or bookings.",{"children":"We may require email verification, identity checks, age confirmation, or additional screening before enabling certain account functions, listings, or bookings."}],["$","p","You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity that occurs under your account.",{"children":"You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity that occurs under your account."}]]}]]}],["$","section","3. User Conduct",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"3. User Conduct"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","You may use Discreet Set only for lawful business purposes related to location discovery, booking, hosting, and production coordination.",{"children":"You may use Discreet Set only for lawful business purposes related to location discovery, booking, hosting, and production coordination."}],["$","p","You may not misuse the platform, harass other users, submit false or misleading information, attempt unauthorized access, scrape protected data, evade safety controls, or use the service to facilitate illegal conduct.",{"children":"You may not misuse the platform, harass other users, submit false or misleading information, attempt unauthorized access, scrape protected data, evade safety controls, or use the service to facilitate illegal conduct."}],["$","p","Users are responsible for acting professionally, respecting property rules, honoring agreed shoot terms, and complying with all applicable laws, permits, contracts, labor rules, zoning rules, and content regulations.",{"children":"Users are responsible for acting professionally, respecting property rules, honoring agreed shoot terms, and complying with all applicable laws, permits, contracts, labor rules, zoning rules, and content regulations."}]]}]]}],["$","section","4. Privacy Tiers",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"4. Privacy Tiers"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Discreet Set offers privacy-based listing tiers to help users manage how much location information is shared before booking.",{"children":"Discreet Set offers privacy-based listing tiers to help users manage how much location information is shared before booking."}],["$","p","Public listings may display broader location and property details. Discrete listings may limit identifying information and reveal fuller details only during the inquiry or approval process. NDA Required listings may require signed confidentiality terms before exact addresses, sensitive visuals, or other identifying details are shared.",{"children":"Public listings may display broader location and property details. Discrete listings may limit identifying information and reveal fuller details only during the inquiry or approval process. NDA Required listings may require signed confidentiality terms before exact addresses, sensitive visuals, or other identifying details are shared."}],["$","p","Hosts choose the privacy tier for their listings, and producers agree to respect any limits on sharing, recording, or disclosing location information provided through the platform.",{"children":"Hosts choose the privacy tier for their listings, and producers agree to respect any limits on sharing, recording, or disclosing location information provided through the platform."}]]}]]}],["$","section","5. Booking & Payments",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"5. Booking & Payments"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Bookings are not final until accepted or confirmed through the platform workflow and any required payment steps are completed.",{"children":"Bookings are not final until accepted or confirmed through the platform workflow and any required payment steps are completed."}],["$","p","Discreet Set charges a total platform fee of 10% per booking. Unless otherwise stated, this total fee may be allocated across the transaction in a manner shown at checkout or in booking details.",{"children":"Discreet Set charges a total platform fee of 10% per booking. Unless otherwise stated, this total fee may be allocated across the transaction in a manner shown at checkout or in booking details."}],["$","p","Users agree to pay all quoted rates, fees, taxes, damage charges, overtime, and any other charges disclosed as part of the booking. Payment processing may be handled by third-party processors subject to their own terms.",{"children":"Users agree to pay all quoted rates, fees, taxes, damage charges, overtime, and any other charges disclosed as part of the booking. Payment processing may be handled by third-party processors subject to their own terms."}]]}]]}],["$","section","6. Cleaning & Property Condition",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"6. Cleaning & Property Condition"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Guests are expected to leave the property in the same condition as found. Reasonable wear is expected, but excessive mess, damage, or unclean conditions will result in a cleaning fee charged to your payment method.",{"children":"Guests are expected to leave the property in the same condition as found. Reasonable wear is expected, but excessive mess, damage, or unclean conditions will result in a cleaning fee charged to your payment method."}],["$","p","Cleaning fees are determined by the host based on:",{"children":"Cleaning fees are determined by the host based on:"}],["$","p","• Time and materials required to restore the property",{"children":"• Time and materials required to restore the property"}],["$","p","• Documented before/after photos",{"children":"• Documented before/after photos"}],["$","p","• Industry-standard cleaning rates",{"children":"• Industry-standard cleaning rates"}],["$","p","Typical cleaning fees range from $100-$500 depending on property size and condition.",{"children":"Typical cleaning fees range from $100-$500 depending on property size and condition."}]]}]]}],["$","section","7. Cancellation Policy",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"7. Cancellation Policy"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Unless a listing or booking states otherwise, cancellations should be made as early as possible through the platform or agreed communication channel.",{"children":"Unless a listing or booking states otherwise, cancellations should be made as early as possible through the platform or agreed communication channel."}],["$","p","Hosts and producers are expected to use commercially reasonable efforts to communicate changes promptly, minimize disruption, and handle refunds or rescheduling in good faith according to the booking terms presented at the time of reservation.",{"children":"Hosts and producers are expected to use commercially reasonable efforts to communicate changes promptly, minimize disruption, and handle refunds or rescheduling in good faith according to the booking terms presented at the time of reservation."}],["$","p","We may establish standard cancellation windows, credits, partial refunds, or exceptions for emergencies, safety concerns, suspected policy violations, or force majeure events.",{"children":"We may establish standard cancellation windows, credits, partial refunds, or exceptions for emergencies, safety concerns, suspected policy violations, or force majeure events."}]]}]]}],["$","section","8. Content Restrictions",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"8. Content Restrictions"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Discreet Set serves users in the adult content industry, but only for legal, consensual, and lawfully produced activity. All users must be at least 18 years old, or the legal age of majority in their jurisdiction, whichever is higher.",{"children":"Discreet Set serves users in the adult content industry, but only for legal, consensual, and lawfully produced activity. All users must be at least 18 years old, or the legal age of majority in their jurisdiction, whichever is higher."}],["$","p","You may not post, request, arrange, promote, or produce illegal content or activities through the platform, including trafficking, exploitation, non-consensual content, underage content, or any other unlawful conduct.",{"children":"You may not post, request, arrange, promote, or produce illegal content or activities through the platform, including trafficking, exploitation, non-consensual content, underage content, or any other unlawful conduct."}],["$","p","Users are solely responsible for ensuring their productions, bookings, and use of any location comply with applicable laws, record-keeping rules, permitting requirements, and contractual obligations.",{"children":"Users are solely responsible for ensuring their productions, bookings, and use of any location comply with applicable laws, record-keeping rules, permitting requirements, and contractual obligations."}]]}]]}],["$","section","9. Intellectual Property",{"className":"rounded-[24px] border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50/70 p-6 sm:p-7","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] text-black","children":"9. Intellectual Property"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-black/80 sm:text-base","children":[["$","p","Discreet Set and its branding, site design, software, text, graphics, and platform content are owned by us or our licensors and are protected by intellectual property laws.",{"children":"Discreet Set and its branding, site design, software, text, graphics, and platform content are owned by us or our licensors and are protected by intellectual property laws."}],["$","p","Users retain ow